\par \endash  }{\f2\fs24\insrsid15757170\charrsid15015538 Ak\'fdch psov? Odtrhli sa z re\'9daz\'ed, be\'9atie!}{\f2\fs24\insrsid3298682  \endash  }{\f2\fs24\insrsid15757170\charrsid15015538 ced\'ed zanovito.
