\par \endash  }{\f2\fs24\insrsid15757170\charrsid15015538 Pozajtra, ale hne\'ef r\'e1no, aspo\'f2 o \'9atvrtej!}{\f2\fs24\insrsid3298682  \endash  }{\f2\fs24\insrsid15757170\charrsid15015538 dolo\'9e\'ed Oliver a vysko\'e8\'ed z dvier.
