\par Slivnick\'fd stoja na pre\'9aovom r\'e1me a pozoruj\'fa Rafaela. Dv\'edha \'9atvorhrann\'e9 dubov\'e9 drevo s dierou v prostried}{\f2\fs24\insrsid7419619\charrsid15015538 k}{\f2\fs24\insrsid15757170\charrsid15015538 u a okut\'e9 navrchu mocnou \'9e
