rskej uniformy! Aj \'e8etn\'edci s\'fa}{\f2\fs24\insrsid3298682  \endash  }{\f2\fs24\insrsid15757170\charrsid15015538 zl\'ed. Pod bod\'e1kmi nah\'e1\'f2aj\'fa Ho\'9at\'e1\'e8ana, ke\'ef na mesteck\'fdch Podolkoch vykope si zemiak alebo vylom\'ed
 klas kukurice, ale prav\'fdch zlodejov}{\f2\fs24\insrsid3298682  \endash  }{\f2\fs24\insrsid15757170\charrsid15015538 R\'f3cha Sv\'e4t\'e9ho a Mikul\'e1\'9aa Habd\'9eu}{\f2\fs24\insrsid3298682  \endash  }{\f2\fs24\insrsid15757170\charrsid15015538 iba pot
